Hanuman or Bajrang Bali is the central diety of Hindu Mythology. He is known for his significant contribution in Mahabharata.
Devotee of Rama and his great admirer.
Hanuman is the God of Power,Intelligence and wisdom .
He is also known as Shiva favourite. Popularly known as the "Rudra Avatar" .
The most practical thing about "hanuman" is that,he is still alive with his body till date. 
As a gift of his service in Mahabharata, he asked Lord Rama to keep him alive till people continue praying "RAM".
Among all the Hindu Diety , He is a very active and listen to his devotee within no time . 
Mainly , his invocation and prayer is very fruitful for Students.
Anybody who needs instantaneous Power with wisdom should pray "Hanuman".